author: dmkarr
msg: Enabled "onclick", "ondblclick", "onmousedown", "onmouseover", "onmousemove", and "onmouseup" attributes in "html-el:img" tag, as the base class supports them.
Added "styleId" attribute to "html:option" and "html-el:option", as the HTML specification specifies that the "id" attribute is legal in "option" elements.
Added comments wrt "html:optionsCollection" and "html:options" indicating that the "styleId" attribute is specifically not supported because of uniqueness constraints for the "id" attribute.
Added a simple test of the "styleId" attribute of "html-el:option" to the strutsel-exercise-taglib application.
